name: Custom Sole-Protector™ by 3M
description:
About the Product:
Sole Phresh has teamed up with the maker of the ultimate protection for your kicks, Sole-Protector™, to bring this amazing product to the Ebay Marketplace for Sneakerheads around the globe.
Sole-Protector™ uses 3M™ adhesive technology to protect your soles! The material is ultra clear, ultra strong urethane. This is not over the counter type film, this is a commercial grade high quality proprietary film specifically produced for the good people at Sole-Protector™. Not only is it great when it comes to keeping lighter colored soles clean, it slows down yellowing significantly on rubber bottoms.
Don't stress, the film is sole friendly and will always come off in one piece without leaving a trace of residue!
 
What you will receive:
 
These custom Sole Protectors are ~13.5"x5.5" (Qty 2) 3M sheet for each of your kicks.  Simply trace the bottoms and cut out or cover areas desired, use the extra to protect even more! Custom SP works for Size 15 and below. All orders will come with a set of installation instructions!
